ExecDesc.value: Corel PDF Fusion XPS Stack Buffer Overflow [IPv6, Version]

EngDesc.value: A code execution vulnerability exists in Corel PDF Fusion. The vulnerability is due to a stack buffer overflow when parsing names in ZIP directory entries of an XPS file. A remote attacker could exploit this vulnerability by enticing a user to open a crafted XPS file. A successful attack would result in execution of arbitrary code in the security context of the affected application.
